@githubjeka the following rule causes the mentioned earlier error. Switching properties to `public` _"solves"_ the problem.

``` php
namespace app\rbac;

use yii\rbac\Rule;

class TestRule extends Rule
{
    public $name = 'rule';

    protected $foo;

    private $bar;

    public function execute($user, $item, $params)
    {
        return true;
    }
}
```
